habits, certain addictions, you know, around smoking, eating, drinking and whatnot.

56
00:08:18,754 --> 00:08:20,596
It's very difficult, you see.

57
00:08:20,615 --> 00:08:26,762
And the more you don't keep your resolve, the more you undermine your ability to keep resolve.

58
00:08:27,904 --> 00:08:31,988
So you have to really keep to your resolve.

59
00:08:32,009 --> 00:08:36,073
Now, you won't keep to resolve if it's not a wise undertaking.

60
00:08:36,315 --> 00:08:41,019
And what we mean by that is that it's something that you actually feel you can do.

61
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:42,601
There's no point in

62
