69
00:09:12,855 --> 00:09:39,251
so after morning chanting here before we say you know before we make the final bounce I always ask people to make a resolution for the day this is more like a general resolve just to live mindfully with a good heart something very general you see now the problem with these

70
00:09:39,804 --> 00:09:43,628
These resolves, of course, we keep forgetting.

71
00:09:43,648 --> 00:09:52,515
So, as often as you can during the day, to keep reinforcing that resolve by just saying it, eventually becomes habitual.

72
