73
00:10:07,148 --> 00:10:09,070
But the vow only lasts as long as the ceremony.

74
00:10:09,707 --> 00:10:11,429
It might last a couple of days after that.

75
00:10:11,630 --> 00:10:13,913
Then you get fed up with each other.

76
00:10:13,933 --> 00:10:15,556
So it's a constant.

77
00:10:16,256 --> 00:10:25,870
