85
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:54,386
So then he wrote back and he said, when I'm playing with my children

86
00:11:55,244 --> 00:12:07,259
and he's got young kids, and he's actually in that sort of communication of being creative with them and all that, then these ideas of being habitual and lack of spontaneity disappear.

87
00:12:07,841 --> 00:12:08,822
