88
00:12:09,081 --> 00:12:12,046
I said, yes.

89
00:12:12,066 --> 00:12:20,998
So this comes about by, you know, recognising what your intentions are, make sure they're wholesome, and then you just do it, you put yourself into it.

90
00:12:23,745 --> 00:12:26,429
And that's one of this business of Adhitana, you see.

91
00:12:36,982 --> 00:12:46,296
So this Adhitana, Resolute Resolution, is a real virtue to develop.

92
00:12:46,316 --> 00:12:50,120
